name: 素裳 - Sushang LORA. / Honkai: Star Rail - 崩壊スターレイル
description:
N°20 Release, 素裳 - Sushang from Honkai: Star Rail - 崩壊スターレイル.

You can now request a Character's LORA. CLICK HERE

Put everything in Filter for seeing all images!

Click on Show more for Weight & Trigger recommendation, Also click on About This Version at Right Corner for more Info.

Well, it's was a challenge & It's was a Request, Well Sushang, Since she's has Very very low Art & IA Art on It, it was a good challenge (Like 14 Images at max in Booru + Pixiv).

But! i did manage & Trained The Lora to get 69+ Images, How ? Simple, i just upscaled, cropped, and flipped the angles of any images & I mixed a little with Game Screencaps at the best quality possible since i upscaled them with 4x-AnimeSharp, i tryed to be the most precise possible on Sushang, i think it will be hard to do better at the moment since Art on it is Very Very Low, But honestly, I'm quite satisfied about the result.

AnimeFullFinalPrunedFP16 used, so he work with the majority of Anime Model.

Flexibility is Ok as you can see in Examples images, best is to put 0.6-0.8 Weight for Flexibility.

About Trigger Words & Prompts: SushangV4 (For Trigger) & for prompts just refer to examples image.

Weight recommended: 0.6-1. - Work at Weight 1, Best result: 0.7-1

Negative Embedding used: EasyNegative, BadPrompt2 and sometime negative_hand-neg.

Leave a Review & Share you're image in comments if you appreciate this Work :).
